testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.CollectoryServiceSpec

testcase.name: new organisations will be registered with the collectory
new projects will be registered with the collectory
updates will be treated as creates if the project does not have a dataResourceId
updates can be performed when a project is edited
MERIT projects will use the MERIT data provider
updates won't be sent if only hiddenJSON data has changed
the institution id will be mapped if an associated organisation has one
